  "instructions": [
    "Heat the butter in a cataplana over medium heat.",
    "Add the minced garlic and sauté for 1 minute.",
    "Add the semolina flour and cook for 2 minutes, stirring constantly.",
    "Gradually add the water, whisking constantly to prevent lumps.",
    "Bring the mixture to a boil, then reduce the heat to low and simmer for 5 minutes.",
    "Stir in the sour cream, dried parsley, salt, and black pepper.",
    "Cook for an additional 2 minutes, or until the pilaf has thickened.",
    "Serve hot, garnished with additional parsley if desired."
